product_name: IT CosmeticsBye Bye Under Eye Full Coverage Anti-Aging Waterproof Concealer
summary: SummaryBye Bye Breakout Full-Coverage Concealer is a waterproof, full coverage concealer that lasts up to 24 hours. Just one dot brightens and smooths dark circles, skin redness, and wrinkles.
details: DetailsBenefitsFULL COVERAGE: Delivers highly pigmented full coverage for up to 24 hours & smooths skinCOLOR CORRECTING: Conceals skin redness, age spots, hyperpigmentation, broken capillaries & helps hide blemishes and wrinklesBRIGHTENING: Conceals dark eye circles and brightens the undereye areaWATERPROOFFeatures93% say product provides full coverage**86% say product corrects the look of imperfections****Results observed in a consumer studyKey IngredientsPeptides: Help reduce the appearance of wrinkles for the look of smoother, firmer skinHydrolyzed Collagen: Amino acid protein known to support skin elasticity for a youthfully smooth appearanceHyaluronic Acid: Helps attract moisture, support skin elasticity and plump the look of fine lines and wrinklesAntioxidants: Help defend against free radical damageItem 2533871How To UseWarm a pinhead-size amount with your fingers and tap onto skin. Can also be worn as a foundation.IngredientsParaffinum Liquidum / Mineral Oil / Huile Minerale, Petrolatum, Vp/Hexadecene Copolymer, Silica Dimethyl Silylate [Nano] / Silica Dimethyl Silylate, Bis-Diglyceryl Polyacyladipate-2, Ozokerite, Phenoxyethanol, Tocopheryl Acetate, Aluminum Hydroxide, Kaolin, Niacinamide, Sodium Hyaluronate, Magnesium Ascorbyl Phosphate, Ascorbyl Palmitate, Hydrolyzed Collagen, Aqua / Water / Eau, Tocopherol, Glycerin, Steareth-20, Chlorhexidine Digluconate, N-Hydroxysuccinimide, Sodium Citrate, Potassium Sorbate, Palmitoyl Tripeptide-1, Chrysin, Palmitoyl Tetrapeptide-7, Citric Acid, Biotin.Shipping & Coupon RestrictionsThis brand is excluded from most Ulta Beauty coupons.See brand eligibility details
how_to_use: Warm a pinhead-size amount with your fingers and tap onto skin. Can also be worn as a foundation.

reviews.headline: Too thick  on my skin.  I am returning it.
reviews.comments: It's too thick for my skin.  Don't like it.

reviews.headline: warm it on your hand before applying
reviews.comments:
This product is SO GOOD. I've been using it for the past 7 years? It's been a perfect color match for me as a medium-neutral undertone and it LASTS. very buildable coverage and it covers my freckles and evens out my complexion very well. I use less foundation because this product helps smooth out so much for me already. 

My biggest tip is to warm/spread product on the back of your hand first before applying to your face so that it isn't too tacky or thick. Love love love

reviews.headline: Love will continue buying
reviews.comments: Was given to me from a family member in a makeup case of makeup. Loved from first use. The writing was faded and I couldn't read what it said. Had to use google lens. Ultra worker instantly knew what I was talking about and helped me find it.

reviews.headline: Ride or Die Product
reviews.comments: I've used this concealer for 12 years. It will always be a staple in my make up bag. Last such a long time and the smallest amount of product goes such a long way. I have very very dark circles and have yet to find a concealer that covere like this does. I love so much that it's waterproof too. It lasts me all day even when working out and sweating or swimming!

reviews.headline: Don't be fooled by the good reviews!!
reviews.comments: Usually I take 1 star reviews with a grain of salt and move on, but please I am telling you do not buy this concealer. It is extremely patchy and flaky and I have oily skin. The application is definitely not well thought out. Don't waste your money!

reviews.headline: Would not buy this product again
reviews.comments: Bought this product because I like waterproof concealer and my favorite Lancome concealer has been discontinued.   Unfortunately, this is just another thick and goopy concealer that has a sheen you have to use powder to try to tone down.

reviews.headline: Very thick
reviews.comments: I have to use a moisturizer first and then a tiny bit of the concealer. It works

reviews.headline: If I had to buy one makeup product and nothing else
reviews.comments:
I have struggled with concealer for so long and have tried so many! I have very dry skin except for that time of the monthâ€¦this concealer is gods gift to this planet and i cannot rave enough about it. The color options the thickness the creaminess, the COVERAGE. I have used this for 2-3 years now and I do not use anything else. It stands alone or blends well with moisturizer or classic with foundation. A little goes a long way and this size is perfect. I normally dont care to buy expensive makeup but this is my holy grail and the only thing i feel cannot be dupe by a drugstore or otherwise. Just get it! I get medium 23.5. Doesn't oxidize even an older bottle and even if left in scorching heat. 
Go darker than lighter if buying online.

reviews.headline: Game changer
reviews.comments: I've been using this product  for about five years. Given genetics and aging I have tried numerous under eye concealers. This is truly the only one that stays on. I also have dry aging skin. I know others have said that's their complaint but if you use it with a primer, it doesn't go on cakey.  I don't have to use a primer all the time, but during winter in Michigan I do.  I play hockey and yes, you don't have to get ready and wear make up for sports but I'm approaching 60 and still like to cover the dark circles! This is the only under eye cover-up that goes on easily and stays put even when you're sweating.

reviews.headline: Great coverage
reviews.comments: I love this product. It has great coverage and matches nicely.

reviews.headline: my one and only < 33
reviews.comments: i have the darkest undereye circles everrrr and ive tried just about every concealer in existence and this one is the ONLY one that actually works!! the way its actually full coverage, actually lasts all day, and actually doesnt crease is INSANE i cant recommend this product enough!! it cosmetics if u ever discontinue this i will claw my eyes out

faceoff_positive.comments: I got a sample of this because nikkietutorials raves about it, and now I see why! I'm definitely going back to purchase the full size! It covers dark circles so well and it help with your bags and wrinkles! Definitely a full coverage concealer!
faceoff_positive.headline: New favorite concealer! Best I've used ever!

faceoff_negative.comments: I really like this product. It is full coverage concealer and that is exactly what I am looking for. However, and this is a BIG however, I am very disappointed with the amount of product in the tube. Don't be fooled by the size of the tube because half of it is air! After opening my first tube, squeezing out all of the air, only half the tube had actual product in it. I thought "this must be a mistake" so I took it back to the store, received an exchange and the exact thing happened with my second tube. Both where brand new, in boxes and completely sealed. For the price I totally expected a full tube of product. The packaging is very deceiving!
faceoff_negative.headline: Great coverage BUT very little product in tube!!!!!
